{
  "texts": [
    "CNN-based models can be sensitive to these factors, leading to decreased recognition accuracy.",
    "Future research could investigate ways to handle the noise and variability in Arabic handwriting to improve recognition accuracy.",
    "• Recognition of diacritics: Recognizing diacritics is important for accurate AHR, but it is a challenging task due to the small size of the marks and their placement above or below letters.",
    "• Real-time recognition: CNN-based models are effective in offline AHR.",
    "However, the demand for real-time recognition is increasing, especially in applications such as mobile devices."
  ]
}